quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  75,31,"Magar usne na sach mana , aur na namaz padhi"
  75,32,Balke jhutlaya aur palat gaya
  75,33,Phir akadta hua apne ghar walon ki taraf chal diya
  75,34,Yeh rawish tere hi liye sazawaar hai aur tujh hi ko zeib deti hai
  75,35,Haan yeh rawish tere hi liye sazawaar hai aur tujh hi ko zeib deti hai
  75,36,"Kya Insan ne yeh samajh rakkha hai ke woh yunhi mohmal (left alone, unquestioned )chodh diya jayega"
  75,37,Kya woh ek hakeer pani ka nutfa (sperm from semen) na tha jo (raham –e-madar mei) tapkaya jata hai
  75,38,"Phir woh ek lothda(clot) bana, phir Allah ne uska jism banaya aur uske aazaa durust kiye"
  75,39,Phir ussey mard aur aurat ki do qismein banayi
  75,40,Kya woh ispar qadir nahin hai ke marne walon ko phir zinda karde